replies.body: At this point in the process, the patch wants to connect to the patching servers to start downloading updates but is failing.  I recommend going over our [connection issues](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) guide to tune up your network and allow that connection to get through!  Let me know if you have any questions!

Thank for the reply,

I believe that I do not have a real internet issue because my other machine which connected to the same wifi does not have issue with updating/installing.

The error seems happens on some local process...
